      "role": "user",
      "content": "it feels like i've tried everything though. the meds, the physical therapy, the doctors... nothing makes it go away. it just feels like i'm trapped in this cage of pain. sometimes i just look at the ceiling and think about how much easier it would be if everything was just... still. if the noise and the burning just stopped forever.",
